{"tid":2508276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小米俾人捉到監控你冚家","createTime":"2021-04-28T15:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T15:27:16.000Z","uid":281306,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"574e5c35c81aa274a2e51d75621f980e7a203bde","tid":2508276,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"話中國設備冇後門嘅人出黎解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家唔單止將你屋企人資料送中，仲送埋你鄰居中呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揭發家中電視被置入監視功能的網民在帖文中指出，他察覺電視畫面傳送速度緩慢，故檢查有甚麼後台服務開著，結果<span class=\"red\">發現有個叫「勾正數據服務」的程式自動運行。該文還說，經過抓包研究發現，該服務把hostname、mac、ip，甚至網絡延遲時間全傳回去了，還探測周圍的wifi SSID名稱、<a href=\"http://mac地址也打包傳到這個gz-data.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmac%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E4%B9%9F%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85%E5%82%B3%E5%88%B0%E9%80%99%E5%80%8Bgz-data.com&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzSWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=310c8422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mac地址也打包傳到這個gz-data.com</a>的域名。</span><br />\n<br />\n而帖文中提及的的「勾正數據服務」，據稱出自<span class=\"red\">北京勾正數據科技有限公司（GozenData）</span>，該公司是中國內地首家智能大屏領域的大數據公司，截至2018年底已覆蓋智能電視終端1.03億部，佔全網設備量55%。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，2019年4月，北京勾正數據科技有限公司的「勾正數據」已與創維、酷開、TCL、長虹、康佳、風行、微鯨、電視貓、三洋、東芝、飛利浦等企業達成長期合作關係，通過在系統層植入SDK，以便獲得智能電視數據採集。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/android-04272021083557.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fandroid-04272021083557.html&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzSWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=299ff9a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/android-04272021083557.html</a>"},{"pid":"f919105601513d4ac4b5bfed84d4b77e184c55a6","tid":2508276,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac886fd629d0804c014448cd806b67b1388d22d","tid":2508276,"uid":265731,"like":1,"